trans-unit.source: Provides an extensibility point for mapping WSDL contracts and policy assertions into [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] standard bindings.
trans-unit.target: Gir et extensibility punkt for tilordning WSDL kontrakter og policydeklarasjon til [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] standard bindinger.

trans-unit.source: Override this class to extend the standard mapping between WSDL and a standard binding.
trans-unit.target: Overstyre denne klassen for å utvide standard tilordningen mellom WSDL og en standard binding.

trans-unit.source: Then attach your custom object to a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter> either programmatically or by using an application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Deretter koble til det egendefinerte objektet til en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter>programmatisk eller ved å bruke en programmets konfigurasjonsfil.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter>

trans-unit.source: You can also attach your custom object to the internal <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter> used by the [ServiceModel Metadata Utility Tool (Svcutil.exe)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) using an application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også knytte egendefinerte-objektet til den interne <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter>brukes av den [ServiceModel Metadata verktøyet verktøyet (Svcutil.exe)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) ved hjelp av en programmets konfigurasjonsfil.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StandardBindingImporter.System%23ServiceModel%23Description%23IWsdlImportExtension%23BeforeImport%2A> method to directly modify the metadata that is then imported into standard binding objects.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StandardBindingImporter.System%23ServiceModel%23Description%23IWsdlImportExtension%23BeforeImport%2A>metode for å endre direkte metadataene som deretter importert til standard binding objekter.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StandardBindingImporter.System%23ServiceModel%23Description%23IWsdlImportExtension%23BeforeImport%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StandardBindingImporter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StandardBindingImporter"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Called prior to importing the metadata documents associated with the standard binding.
trans-unit.target: Kalles før du importerer i metadata-dokumenter som er knyttet til standard bindingen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.BeforeImport%2A> methods of all registered <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension> objects is called before anything is imported from the supplied metadata.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.BeforeImport%2A>metoder for alle registrerte <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension>objekter kalles før noe er importert fra de angitte metadataene.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.BeforeImport%2A>

trans-unit.source: At this point, you can directly modify the metadata that is subsequently imported into standard binding objects.
trans-unit.target: Nå kan du endre metadata importeres senere til standard bindingen objekter direkte.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection%601> of type <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"></xref> that contains the policy elements.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection%601> av typen <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"> </xref> som inneholder policyelementer.

trans-unit.source: Provides an extensibility point for importing WSDL contract information for standard bindings.
trans-unit.target: Gir et extensibility punkt som kan importeres WSDL Kontraktsinformasjon om standard bindinger.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter"></xref> for importing and resolving WSDL metadata.

trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext"> </xref> som inneholder konteksten for konvertering fra WSDL tjenestebeskrivelsen.

trans-unit.source: Provides an extensibility point for mapping endpoints defined in WSDL into the service description.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder et extensibility punkt for tilordning av endepunkt som er definert i WSDL i tjenestebeskrivelsen.
